

ON THE ROAD TO FINANCIAL RUIN?
AND IF SO, WHICH SIDE ARE THEY
DRIVING ON?
THEN PROTESTERS TRY TO SHUT DOWN
WALL STREET, THOUGH IF THEY GIVE
THEM THE TIME, WALL STREET MIGHT
DO IT FOR THEM.
AND MY GUEST DANIEL YERGIN HAS A
NEW BOOK ABOUT THE FUTURE OF
ENERGY.
I HOPE WE FUEL OUR FACTORIES BY
BURNING BOOKS.
[LAUGHTER]
THE FEDERAL RESERVE WANTS TO
STIMULATE THE ECONOMY.
WELL THEN BEN BERNANKE'S GOING
TO HAVE TO SHOW A LITTLE LEG.
THIS IS "THE COLBERT REPORT."

